83
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:53,830
However, if you look at the paper, the
paper presented that information.

84
00:04:53,830 --> 00:04:56,210
It also presented the relative risk.

85
00:04:56,210 --> 00:04:58,364
And the relative risk here was 1.26.

86
00:04:58,364 --> 00:05:00,970
The interpretation would be that there

87
00:05:00,970 --> 00:05:05,580
