102
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,870
the hormone group, 30 per 10,000 in the
placebo group.

103
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:06,520
So seven additional heart attacks per
10,000 women-years.

104
00:06:06,520 --> 00:06:09,016
But again, the relative risk, if you look
at it as a relative risk.

105
00:06:09,016 --> 00:06:10,168
Is 1.29.

106
00:06:10,168 --> 00:06:15,520
That again looks much more dramatic, but
in fact a much more honest presentation of

107
00:06:15,520 --> 00:06:19,230
the risks would be to say, to look at the
absolute risk differences, or the absolute

108
00:06:19,230 --> 00:06:23,420
rate difference here, 0.07% again is not
