113
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:42,680
So, if it's seven additional heart attacks
are going to occur when you

114
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:45,750
treat 10,000 women with hormones for one
year.

115
00:06:45,750 --> 00:06:49,070
Then to harm one woman, you would need to,
so

