123
00:07:14,750 --> 00:07:18,720
Now this is, that's a pretty high number
needed to harm, or number needed to treat.

124
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:22,340
But remember, if you have 14 million women
on hormones,

125
00:07:22,340 --> 00:07:25,610
that translates to several thousand cases
